---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section
  class="relative py-32 md:py-48 bg-background overflow-hidden group/philosophy"
>
  <!-- Immersive Background Image -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <img
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1452587925148-ce544e77e70d?q=80&w=2560&auto=format&fit=crop"
      alt="Fondo de Filosofía"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30 group-hover/philosophy:scale-105 transition-transform duration-10000 ease-linear"
    />
    <!-- Fixed Overlay Gradients -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-b from-background via-transparent to-background"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-r from-background via-transparent to-background"
    >
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-12">
      <!-- Decorative Icon Section -->
      <div
        class="flex justify-center motion-translate-y-in-20 motion-opacity-in-0 motion-duration-1000"
      >
        <div class="relative">
          <Icon
            name="lucide:quote"
            class="w-16 h-16 text-primary/20 rotate-12 absolute -top-8 -left-8"
          />
          <div
            class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full border border-primary/30 flex items-center justify-center bg-primary/5 backdrop-blur-sm relative z-10"
          >
            <Icon
              name="lucide:heart"
              class="w-8 h-8 text-primary animate-pulse-slow"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Main Quote -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <span
          class="inline-block text-primary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] motion-opacity-in-0 motion-duration-1000 motion-delay-200"
        >
          Nuestra Esencia
        </span>
        <h2
          class="text-4xl md:text-7xl font-serif font-bold text-foreground leading-[1.1] motion-translate-y-in-50 motion-opacity-in-0 motion-duration-1000 motion-delay-400"
        >
          "No tomamos fotos, <br />
          <span class="text-primary italic">hacemos</span> fotos."
        </h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Descriptive Text with Glassmorphism Box -->
      <div
        class="relative max-w-2xl mx-auto p-2 motion-translate-y-in-50 motion-opacity-in-0 motion-duration-1000 motion-delay-600"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute -inset-4 bg-primary/5 backdrop-blur-md rounded-3xl -z-10 border border-white/10 hidden md:block"
        >
        </div>
        <p
          class="text-lg md:text-xl text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed italic"
        >
          En LensCraft, creemos que cada imagen debe evocar una emoción. Más
          allá de la técnica, buscamos la conexión humana, la luz perfecta y el
          instante irrepetible que define un recuerdo para siempre.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Brand Signature Hint -->
      <div
        class="pt-8 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 motion-opacity-in-0 motion-duration-1000 motion-delay-800"
      >
        <div class="w-px h-12 bg-linear-to-b from-primary to-transparent"></div>
        <span class="font-serif italic text-foreground opacity-60"
          >LensCraft Studio</span
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes pulse-slow {
    0%,
    100% {
      opacity: 0.5;
      transform: scale(1);
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: scale(1.1);
    }
  }
  .animate-pulse-slow {
    animation: pulse-slow 3s infinite ease-in-out;
  }
</style>
